A '''haberdasher''' was a dealer in [[Gender/Legends|men's]] clothing.

In [[8 ABY/Legends|8 ABY]], [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] sought the services of a haberdasher to quickly provide him with civilian formal attire for a state dinner.

